  <Notes>This encounter is run in two parts, as described on pages 22 and 23.  In the first half of the fight, EV-8D3 uses two groups of B1 battle droids for ranged attacks, while sending in the PK worker droids to fight melee PCs.  When half of this force is destroyed, they retreat into the cargo room and the first encounter ends.  The second encounter starts when the PCs enter the cargo room.  It will consist of the droids that are left from the first encounter, plus the remaining droids in the encounter.[P]
In the second half, R2-B7 will head to the freighter to prep it for flight.  For the freighter, add whatever light freighter you might want to use for the encounter, and create a roster for it.  If they manage to pick up Lookout, he'll be the pilot and gunner, and should be added to the encounter as such.</Notes>
